Aseries of top-flight games involving elite European teams across various footballs, competitions will be aired live on GOtv during this week. The games scheduled Saturday will be broadcast live on SuperSport Football (GOtv channel 31) to GOtv Jolli and Max customers and on SuperSport LaLiga (GOtv channel 32) exclusive to GOtv Max customers. At the peak of the pack is the match fixture of the 2020/2021 UEFA Nations League between Ukraine and Switzerland at Arena L’viv stadium. The game kicks off at 7:45pm tonight and will be aired live on SuperSport Football, GOtv channel 31. GOtv’s coverage of the Nations League will continue tomorrow when Denmark take on Belgium in the Nations League match which airs live at 7:45pm on SuperSport LaLiga, GOtv channel 32.